name: Dip Up
description:
Game controls:

Tap with your left mouse button

Description:

Press to jolt down on soft body obstacles. Jump on jellies!

Make bigger highscores and unlock cooler jelly skins!

Earn stars and buy more soft bodies - different experience and challenge with different soft body skins.

Reach next levels with higher difficulty. Beat your highscore and be cool😎

Game Features:

-Not a randomly generated levels, with finish point(reach 999 points to complete the game)

-Jelly world

-One tap control

-Numerous fun jelly skins

Please support me if you liked the game. Each dollar is appreciated:)
